Powers.DescLong: You quickly fire a round from one of your pistols. The ammunition used contains a special toxin which causes additional toxic damage to the target, but the levels are insufficient to weaken their body.

Powers.DescShort: Ranged, Moderate DMG(Lethal), Minor DoT (Toxic), Knockdown (Foe), -DMG(Foe,All)
Powers.DescLong: You fire a round from each of your pistols. The ammunition used contains a special toxin which causes additional toxic damage to the target and reduces their damage. There is also a chance the target may be knocked down.

Powers.DescShort: Ranged, Hold (Foe), Chance for Superior DMG(Toxic), -Regen(Foe), -Rec(Foe)
Powers.DescLong: You fire a particularly potent round at your opponent. This round is full of toxins which catalyze those introduced by your other attacks. In addition to paralyzing your opponent, these catalysts may alter the toxins in the target's bloodstream, causing additional damage and reducing their regeneration and recovery.

Powers.DescShort: Ranged, -DMG(Foe, All), -DEF(Foe, All), -RES(Foe, Status Effects), -ToHit(Foe), -Heal(Foe), -End(Foe), Chance for High DMG(Toxic), Stun
Powers.DescLong: You fire a particularly potent round at your opponent. This round is full of toxins which catalyze those introduced by your other attacks. In addition to significantly weakening your opponent, these catalysts may alter the toxins in the target's bloodstream, causing additional damage and stunning them.
